# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 4. CONNECT TOPOLOGY — luồng giao tiếp 2 server
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@flow_user_tam_luxury_to_kernel
  Step 1:  User Tâm Luxury (browser/app)
           → mở UI từ nattos-server/apps/tam-luxury/index.html
  
  Step 2:  UI client connect SSE
           → localhost:3001/mach/heyna (nattos-server Node)
  
  Step 3:  Server Node nhận event → relay
           → SmartLink HeyNa transport (per Memory #4)
           → 127.0.0.1:3002 (Rust nauion-host kernel)
  
  Step 4:  Rust kernel xử lý cell logic
           → emit Nauion phản ứng
           → ngược về Node :3001
  
  Step 5:  Node relay lại UI
           → localhost:3001/mach/heyna SSE → user

@transport_canonical_per_memory_4
  HeyNa  → cells (transport giữa cells, qua Rust kernel)
  EventBus  → client (nội bộ UI components, browser)
  SmartLink  → colony (inter-colony, cấp Server-to-Server)

